Attribution Notice (requested, not required):

If you use buffee in your project, we'd appreciate (but don't require)
attribution in one of these forms:

- A "Powered by buffee" note in your application's about page or footer
- A mention in your project's documentation or README
- A link to https://github.com/user/buffee (update with actual URL)

Example attribution:
  "Text editing powered by buffee (https://github.com/user/buffee)"

This attribution request is not a license requirement - it's simply a kind
gesture we appreciate. The Apache 2.0 license governs all usage rights.
